        <description>&lt;i&gt;Tekblast&lt;/i&gt; is an enhanced remake of &lt;a href="/game/bomberman"&gt;Dyna Blaster&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The player's task is to make a way through obstacles, eliminate desired number of opponents with bombs and stay alive. During the game several kinds of items may appear. Some of them may help (for example: boots that let you walk faster, walking through the wall, additional bombs) and some of them can make the task more complicated (for example: various blasts, players positions change, lights off).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The game allows up to three players. In 'multiplayer mode' all players fight each other until only one stays alive. In 'single player mode' the player must find the next level entrance before the time runs out. In addition various opponents appear.</description>
